title: Episode 196: J.W.A. Jackin' With Attitude (Feat. Khadeen and Devale Ellis)
itunes:title: Episode 196: J.W.A. Jackin' With Attitude (Feat. Khadeen and Devale Ellis)
description:
Khadeen and Devale Ellis join the ladies of Lip Service this week as their marriage is put to the test! Devale leaves the room while the ladies ask Khadeen questions about their relationship. Is Devale able to answer these questions correctly upon his return? The crew also discuss topics including monogamy, working through cheating, and even shitting yourself...or all over the place. Enjoy! ***LIVE SHOW ALERT*** Wednesday, June 19, 2019 Sony Hall NYC https://www.sonyhall.com/events/angela-yee/
